page.title: 18TREE SURVEY.
page.content: Survey of Trees and Shrubs. Our survey took place in Leyton during the months of May and June,1985.The area we looked at closely was surrounded by Leyton High Road,Lea Bridge Road and Church Road.We studied all of the trees and shrubs in these streets .We were unable to study the trees and shrubs in peoples back gardens.We tried to find aerial photographs of Leyton to agree our findings but we found this impossible. These are our results: 1166 shrubs 376 saplings 282 young trees 363 mature trees 13 dead trees
